"Orlando Pirates are reportedly set to welcome a new staff member in former Stellenbosch FC Head of Recruitment Brendon Fourie.\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4245, \"end\": 4252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piracy\", \"score\": 0.999991332548962, \"rank\": 8.667526107485072e-06, \"text\": \"Pirates\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piracy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piracy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Masindi Nemtajela was stretched off during Orlando Pirates' 6-0 win over TS Galaxy on Sunday afternoon in Mbombela.\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4365, \"end\": 4372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\", \"score\": 0.9976751427841194, \"rank\": 0.002330274771820797, \"text\": \"Masindi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\"}, {\"begin\": 4438, \"end\": 4447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TS Galaxy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 4471, \"end\": 4479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.849355946257865e-21, \"text\": \"Mbombela\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IT support is not just technical, it is personal.\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Liema Pantsi's victory was clouded as fans of the 'Big Brother Mzansi' show expressed that Smash Afrika was unprofessional towards her.\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4584, \"end\": 4595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\"